  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "titleStrip",
        "attrs": {
          "removable": true
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Coffee Order"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "body",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Indeed, this is a normal paragraph and feels like it."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "[94]"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ">> ئەمە خەو نیە — سوریالە"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "This is not a dream — it's surreal. Nali's reality separates from the audience's reality. This scene is 2 minutes — short and dry and terrifying."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "[95]"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ">> بوکەڵەکە = گەشە. سەمایەکە = ئەو سەمایەیە"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The puppet = Gesha. The dance = the same dance from Scene 43a. Everything spirals back. But this time — there's fire."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "[97]"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ">> ئێستا لەناکاو هەموو شتێک مانا ئەدات"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "C1: Now suddenly everything makes sense. That gardener in Scene 2 — he was talking all along — describing the same events. The audience now knows: what \"watched you\" from Scene 2 onward — was Nali, was Nali's fear, was Nali's world — but in imagination. The entire film was Nali's imagination to see what would happen if that event happ"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "sceneFrame",
            "attrs": {
              "id": "scene-7f2a",
              "number": 1,
              "headingStyle": null,
              "innerDoc": {
                "type": "doc",
                "attrs": {
                  "notes": "Establish mood. Camera stays wide.",
                  "revisionFlag": null
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "sceneLine",
                    "attrs": {
                      "setting": "INT.",
                      "time": "NIGHT"
                    },
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "CAFÉ"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "action",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "A dimly lit café. Rain streaks the windows. "
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Sarah",
                        "marks": [
                          {
                            "type": "tag",
                            "attrs": {
                              "tagType": "character",
                              "entityId": "ent-sarah"
                            }
                          }
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": " sits alone."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "character",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "SARAH"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "dialogue",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "I've been waiting for an hour.",
                        "marks": [
                          {
                            "type": "revisionFlag",
                            "attrs": {
                              "reason": "Punchier?",
                              "status": "open",
                              "createdAt": null
                            }
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
